boxes-and-lines Microservices Architecture

tag Team t
  Backend(blue)
  Frontend(green)
  Platform(purple)

active-tag Team

API Gateway [gateway] | t: Backend, description: Routes all external traffic
  -auth-> AuthService
  -/api-> UserService
  -/products-> ProductService

AuthService | t: Backend, description: OAuth2 and session management
  -validates-> SessionCache
  -reads-> UserDB

UserService | t: Backend
  -reads-> UserDB
  -publishes-> EventBus

ProductService | t: Frontend, description: Catalog search and filtering
  -queries-> ProductDB
  -checks-> ProductCache

EventBus [queue] | t: Platform
  -notifies-> NotificationWorker

NotificationWorker | t: Backend
  -> EmailGateway

[AWS us-east-1]
  [Compute]
    API Gateway
    AuthService
    UserService
    ProductService
    NotificationWorker
  [Data]
    UserDB [database] | t: Platform
    ProductDB [database] | t: Platform
    SessionCache [cache] | t: Platform
    ProductCache [cache] | t: Platform

EmailGateway [external] | t: Backend, description: SendGrid integration

WebApp [frontend] | t: Frontend
WebApp -> API Gateway

Admin [actor] | t: Backend
Admin -> API Gateway
